{"ts": "2026-03-28T08:43:55.002489+00:00", "event_type": "claude", "agent": "Claude", "action": "Bash", "detail": "gh pr create --base dev --head feat/dashboard-tab-enhancements --title \"feat(dashboard): enhance all tabs \u2014 PR merge, agent stats, DB sort/CSV, memo search, structured deploy/decisions\" --body \"$(cat <<'EOF'\n## Summary\n\n- **Overview**: auto-refresh toggle (30s), inline CI check badges (N/N passed) per PR, one-click **Merge** button for CI-green PRs targeting `dev`\n- **Agents**: per-agent activity count + last-action time from `ACTIVITY.log`; activity summary grid when no agent selected  \n- **Memo Center**: PENDING count badge in tab header, inbox keyword search/filter\n- **Database**: clickable column sort (asc/desc toggle), CSV export for table view and SQL query results\n- **Decisions**: stats cards (total, this week, latest date), date label on each entry\n- **Deployments**: env-aware structured view (mainnet/prod/staging/testnet/dev badges), status badges, overview stats\n- **server.js**: fix broken `GET /api/github/pr/:number/checks` (was passing PR number as SHA), add `POST /api/github/pr/:number/merge`, add `GET /api/activity/agents`\n\n## Test plan\n- [ ] TypeScript: `npx tsc --noEmit` \u2192 0 errors \u2705\n- [ ] Build: `npm run build` \u2192 clean \u2705  \n- [ ] Overview tab: enable auto-refresh, confirm panels remount every 30s\n- [ ] Open PR with all-green CI targeting `dev` \u2192 confirm merge button appears; click to merge\n- [ ] Agents tab: confirm activity counts + \"Xm ago\" timestamps per agent\n- [ ] Database tab: click column header to sort; Export CSV button downloads file\n- [ ] Memo Center: send a memo, confirm PENDING count shows in INBOX header; search filters results\n- [ ] Decisions tab: stats cards render with correct totals\n- [ ] Deployments tab: env/status badges render; env filter buttons work\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\nEOF\n)\" 2>&1", "status": "ok"}
