{"ts": "2026-03-28T09:17:23.136295+00:00", "event_type": "claude", "agent": "Claude", "action": "Bash", "detail": "gh issue create --title \"feat(dashboard): comprehensive agent dashboard \u2014 Security tab, Issues tab, health monitor, doc freshness, phase gates, releases\" --label \"enhancement\" --body \"$(cat <<'EOF'\n## Agent team consultation \u2014 required dashboard features\n\nBased on a full read of all 22 agent role files, the following dashboard enhancements are needed:\n\n### New Tabs\n- **Security** \u2014 Phase security gates (from SECURITY.md), CVE suppressions, active findings\n- **Issues** \u2014 Label-filtered GitHub issues (Backend/SDK/Security/QA/DevOps/Docs/Audit)\n\n### New Panels\n- **Backend /health monitor** \u2014 poll backend health endpoint, show db/version/status (Overview)\n- **Doc Freshness** \u2014 parse HEALTH.md freshness table, color FRESH/STALE/EXPIRED (Governance)\n- **Known Gaps** \u2014 parse HEALTH.md critical gaps table (Phases)\n- **Phase Progress (rich)** \u2014 from HEALTH.md with lead agent + blocking issues (Phases)\n- **GitHub Releases** \u2014 version history from GitHub Releases API (Deployments)\n\n### Bug Fix\n- `server.js /api/deployments` reads wrong path \u2014 `docs/agents/DEPLOYMENTS.md` should be `docs/agents/ops/DEPLOYMENTS.md`\n\n### Server additions\n- Label filter on `/api/github/issues?labels=X`\n- `GET /api/github/releases`\n- `GET /api/healthcheck` (proxy to backend :3001/health)\n\nCloses when PR is merged.\nEOF\n)\" 2>&1", "status": "ok"}
